# Assets pipeline

## Scripts (`package.json`)

- `npm run dev` ‚Äî webpack watch + gulp
- `npm run build` ‚Äî webpack + gulp production
- `npm run deploy:dev` / `deploy:prod` ‚Äî SFTP (`deploy.local.env`); `/deploy-dev` (fast, no push), `/deploy-prod` (dev‚Üímain‚Üíprod)
- `npm start` ‚Äî gulp only

## Webpack entries ‚Üí `assets/dist/js/`

| Entry | Source |
|-------|--------|
| `main` | `assets/src/js/main.js` |
| `ajaxFilter` | `assets/src/js/ajax-filter.js` |
| `ajaxSlider` | `assets/src/js/ajax-load-cpt.js` |

`main.js` imports `_generalScripts.js` (sliders, tabs, YouTube) and `prices-calculator.js`.

## SCSS (`assets/src/scss/main.scss`)

`abstracts/` ‚Üí `base/` ‚Üí `components/` ‚Üí `layout/` ‚Üí `pages/` (per template: `front-page/`, `single-offer/`, `_prices-page.scss`, etc.) ‚Üí `vendors/`.

Output: `assets/dist/css/main.css` (+ some page-specific CSS if built separately).

## Enqueued (`configure/js-css.php`)

Bootstrap 4 CDN, Typekit, `main.css`, jQuery, Popper, Bootstrap JS, `vendors.js`, `main.js`. Conditional: `ajaxFilter.js`, `ajaxSlider.js`. Fancybox from `configure.php`.

## Hero slider (homepage)

- ACF `main_slider` on front page
- PHP: `utilities.php` helpers + `template-parts/front-page/hero-slider.php`
- JS: `hero-slider.js` via `__sliders.js` (Swiper 11)
- SCSS: `pages/front-page/_hero-slider.scss`

## Legacy

`templates/` at repo root is an old prototype ‚Äî not used in live hierarchy. `static/` has legacy assets.
